<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>텔레그램 로그인 · 모임 테일보드</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    .login-page { max-width: 400px; margin: 48px auto; text-align: center; }
    .login-page .card { padding: 32px; }
    .login-widget-wrap { display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 24px 0; min-height: 44px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="brand">
        <a href="/">모임 테일보드</a><% if (username) { %> <span class="brand-username">(<%= username %>)</span><% } %>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <% if (canChooseTenant) { %><a href="/">공동체 선택</a><% } %>
        <% if (isAdmin) { %><a href="/admin">관리</a><% } %>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>
  <main class="container">
    <div class="login-page">
      <div class="card">
        <h1>텔레그램으로 로그인</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">참여 시 본인 확인·수정에 사용됩니다.</p>
        <div class="login-widget-wrap">
          <script async src="https://telegram.org/js/telegram-widget.js?22"
                  data-telegram-login="<%= botName %>"
                  data-size="large"
                  data-auth-url="<%= authUrl %>"
                  data-request-access="write">
          </script>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top: 16px;"><a href="/">← 돌아가기</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
